  "texts": [
    "We observed that under the visual context setting, the BLIP-2 model failed to generate any stories.",
    "To train the (+LLAMA 2) version, we adapted the model's dimensionality from 768 to 4096.",
    "We used a batch size of 2 and trained the model for 18 epochs-3 for the pre-task adaptation and 15 for the downstream task training.",
    "We used the 4-bit quantized pre-trained version of (+LLAMA 2) 7B and employed LoRA fine-tuning.",
    "We configured the fine-tuning with a scaling parameter of α = 8 and a rank of r = 8, based on the evidence provided in Hu et al. (2022)."
  ],
